{"tid":960503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗婆婆被搶手袋 熱心人助擒南亞賊","createTime":"2018-12-29T13:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T14:20:46.000Z","uid":42188,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96239379dca8362f6a84c4e92f34e5bc527f1e3a","tid":960503,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"元朗發生搶劫案，下午近3時，一名婆婆於教育路1號攤檔選購蔬果期間，一名南亞男子突然走近並搶去婆婆的手袋，然後拔足逃跑。婆婆見狀大聲呼救，有熱心人士尾隨追截賊人，終成功將賊人擒獲，起回所有失物。警員其後趕至，將賊人拘捕帶署調查。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定係個別例子，我認識嘅南亞人都好nice</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2a246d93283cbf31de0303eb94934c4bf467868","tid":960503,"uid":212317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"南亞個個都係聖人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60af9f006910b887e9a826d1849963d42746500c","tid":960503,"uid":48286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蝻亞賤狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a63882d1c1c5569cd0b273b555c7de990d9b1ea","tid":960503,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"廢老就咪撚幫啦，你話90後我就幫硬。"},{"pid":"bc61d9ba54ebdcb9ffa559d6d9d36597936f244e","tid":960503,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a63882d1c1c5569cd0b273b555c7de990d9b1ea","tid":960503,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"廢老就咪撚幫啦，你話90後我就幫硬。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"兩個都唔抵幫<br />\n但南亞佬係更加低賤既生物"},{"pid":"ec7cb045a2a32ca65b62cc2c14353fce1e1f54f9","tid":960503,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc61d9ba54ebdcb9ffa559d6d9d36597936f244e","tid":960503,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a63882d1c1c5569cd0b273b555c7de990d9b1ea","tid":960503,"uid":153811,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"ci